    "friendshipSealRule": {
      "requiredRank": "A",
      "requiresSameGender": true,
      "commitsToSingleFriend": false,
      "bottleneck": "missable_class_access",
      "note": "Corrin can use a Friendship Seal with every same-gender unit who reaches A support; Corrin does not choose one A+ partner. Plan around class trees that are absent from the route, lost with an unrecruited or permanently departed donor, or otherwise unavailable before the support can reach A.",
      "noteZhHans": "神威可与每一位达到 A 支援的同性别单位使用友情之证；神威无需固定一名 A+ 搭档。请提前规划：某些职业树可能在该路线不存在，或因捐赠单位未被招募、永久离队而失去，或在支援达到 A 之前无法获得。"
    },
